DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260318T000000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260321T235959
DTSTAMP:20260313T222334
CREATED:20250905T193246Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260206T170333Z
UID:10000038-1773792000-1774137599@emersontheatres.org
SUMMARY:NEWFEST: SHORT WORKS 2026
DESCRIPTION:NEWFEST: SHORT WORKS 2026\n\n\n\n\nA festival of short plays written\, directed\, and performed by Emerson College Performing Arts students. \n\n\n\nPLEASE NOTE: This is a free event. Guests will be seated on a first-come\, first-served basis upon arrival. Reserving your tickets does not necessarily guarantee admission\, but we rarely turn anyone away from our free events. Please plan to arrive early—ideally 20 to 30 minutes before showtime—to ensure entry. \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nTo reserve your tickets\, please fill out this form: \n\n\n\nTickets\n\n\n\n\n\nDates\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nEvent Info\n\n\n\nTo reserve your tickets\, please fill out this form: \n\n\n\nTickets\n\n\n\nVenue\n\n\n\n\n\nDetails\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n1 Hour 45 Mins \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nAge 12+ \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nFree with RSVP \n\n\n\n\n\nHealth & Safety Information
URL:https://emersontheatres.org/event/newfest-short-works-2026/
LOCATION:Semel Theatre\, 10 Boylston Pl\, Boston\, Massachusetts\, 02116\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://emersontheatres.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/81/2025/09/NewWorksThumb.png
END:VEVENT
